TNK-BP is offering to sell 100,000
metric tons of ESPO crude for loading June 1 to June 10,
according to a tender document obtained by  Bloomberg News .  The tender closes today at 2 p.m. Moscow time and bids must
be valid until 6 p.m. in London tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
